query:
INSERT INTO v0.logs (chain_id, block_hash, data, height, time)
            SELECT unnest($1::int[]), unnest($2::text[]), unnest($3::jsonb[]), unnest($4::int[]), unnest($5::timestamptz[])
            ON CONFLICT (chain_id, block_hash) DO 
            UPDATE SET
                data = excluded.data,
                height = excluded.height,
                time = excluded.time
